sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Web Interface
    participant Gen as Bullet Generator
    participant Val as AMOT Validator
    participant Queue as Suggestion Queue
    participant Preview as Live Preview
    participant Store as Memory Store
    
    User->>UI: Import Job Description
    UI->>Gen: Analyze JD + Profile
    Gen->>Val: Generate 5 bullets
    Val->>Val: Validate AMOT format
    Val->>Queue: Queue 4 valid bullets
    Note over Val,Queue: 1 bullet failed validation
    
    Queue->>UI: Display suggestions
    UI->>User: Show bullets (4 of 5 valid)
    
    User->>UI: Accept Bullet 1
    UI->>Store: Save accepted bullet
    Store->>Preview: Update preview
    Preview->>UI: Render updated resume
    UI->>User: Show live preview
    
    User->>UI: Reject Bullet 2
    UI->>Queue: Remove from queue
    Note over Queue: Deleted immediately
    
    User->>UI: Edit Bullet 3
    UI->>Val: Re-validate edited text
    Val->>UI: Validation passed
    User->>UI: Accept edited bullet
    UI->>Store: Save edited bullet
    Store->>Preview: Update preview
    
    User->>UI: Request regeneration
    UI->>Gen: Generate 3 more bullets
    Gen->>Val: Validate new bullets
    Val->>Queue: Queue 2 valid bullets
    
    User->>UI: Accept Bullet 4
    UI->>Store: Save accepted bullet
    Store->>Preview: Final update
    
    User->>UI: Export resume
    UI->>Preview: Render to PDF/DOCX
    Preview->>User: Download file
    
    Note over User,Store: Only accepted bullets<br/>appear in exports
